data.description: Look no more this is the one!  This three-bedroom, one-bathroom ranch boasts a newer roof, furnace and water heater.  Plenty of room to run in this HUGE fenced backyard.  Enjoy lazy evenings and summer barbecues on the deck. Nicely landscaped and well maintained this gem won't last long.  Turn key move-in-ready home is waiting for you.  Seller will provide the City Certificate of Occupancy prior to closing.
